data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom gem on a corner lot! This updated residence features a modern interior, perfect for comfortable living. The property comes complete with a very large two-story garage, offering ample space for parking or creative projects. Enjoy the privacy of a fully fenced yard, equipped with automatic sprinklers for easy maintenance. Whether you're seeking a cozy family home or a stylish retreat, this property has it all. Don't miss the chance to make it yours.
